# Treatments tried — {{condition_name}}

Class-by-class catalog of every treatment ever tried. Each row is classified per the adequacy categories in `meta/standards.md`.

## Format

```
### {Class name}

| Treatment | Dates | Dose / intensity | Duration | Adequacy | Outcome / why stopped | Source |
|-----------|-------|------------------|----------|----------|----------------------|--------|
| ...       |       |                  |          |          |                      |        |
```

Adequacy categories: adequate failure / inadequate trial / intolerable / partial response / tachyphylactic response / confounded / unclear / never tried. See `meta/standards.md`.

